\ls1\ilvl0
\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The kids that studied did better\'85intelligence only took you so far\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Kids that practiced their sport did great\'85athleticism only takes you so far\
